videos.description: Devon Daniels tallies a quick 10 points before the 10-minute mark of the first half for NC State against Duke.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Daniels comes out scorching hot for NC State) 2020/2/19

videos.headline: Daniels comes out scorching hot for NC State

videos.description: Devon Daniels' flashy save lands in the hands of DJ Funderburk, who takes Vernon Carey Jr. to the cup for a lay-in.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Daniels' behind-the-back save leads to NC State bucket) 2020/2/19

videos.headline: Daniels' behind-the-back save leads to NC State bucket

videos.description: Cassius Stanley puts on a dribbling exhibition on his way to a nifty finish for Duke, plus the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Duke's Stanley swerves through traffic on Eurostep finish) 2020/2/19

videos.headline: Duke's Stanley swerves through traffic on Eurostep finish

videos.description: Markell Johnson lofts a perfect pass for DJ Funderburk's alley-oop spike.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Funderburk brings thunder and lightning on NC State alley-oop) 2020/2/19

videos.headline: Funderburk brings thunder and lightning on NC State alley-oop

videos.description: Markell Johnson's prayer is pure as he beats the first-half buzzer to extend the Wolfpack's lead over Duke.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (NC State's Johnson opens the bank on half-court buzzer-beater) 2020/2/19

videos.headline: NC State's Johnson opens the bank on half-court buzzer-beater

videos.description: DJ Funderburk receives a shooter's roll on a 3-pointer, and Coach K is seen in disgust over Duke's double-digit deficit.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Everything is falling for NC State, and Coach K can't believe it) 2020/2/19

videos.headline: Everything is falling for NC State, and Coach K can't believe it

videos.description: NC State takes down Duke at home and the student section floods the floor in celebration.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (NC State fans storm court after upset over Duke) 2020/2/19

videos.headline: NC State fans storm court after upset over Duke

videos.description: Markell Johnson's career high of 28 points and Devon Daniels' 25 power NC State's upset of Duke at home.

videos.headline: Johnson, Daniels tag team to take down Duke in upset

videos.description: Mike Krzyzewski calls basketball a "human-being game," and claims NC State was the hungrier team than Duke.
